        q: 'A reader said: "This travel writing is self-indulgent — the writer is more interested in their own feelings and reactions than in genuinely informing us about Rajasthan." To what extent do you agree? Evaluate how successfully the writer balances personal experience with informative content. Support your answer with references to the text.',
